'''Yargh'un pits'''&mdash;also known as '''charnel pits'''&mdash;were large holes that had been dug around [[Shimrra's Citadel|the Citadel]] of [[Shimrra Jamaane]], the [[Supreme Overlord]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Created during Shimrra's purge of the [[Jeedai heresy|''Jeedai'' heresy]], these pits were filled with [[Tooth/Legends|toothy]] [[yargh'un]] creatures, who fed on the corpses of those Yuuzhan Vong who had been condemned to [[Death/Legends|death]] for heresy&mdash;sometimes even those who were still alive. How many pits were carved out was unknown, however Shimrra was willing to build more to house the dead. These pits also served to relax Shimrra, as he found the screams to be soothing while he communed with the [[Yun'o|Gods]].

